sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant CA as Cloud Armor
    participant CW as caller-worker<br/>(gateway-vm :3111)
    participant E as iii-engine<br/>(gateway-vm :49134)
    participant IW as inference-worker<br/>(inference-vm)
    participant M as Gemma 3 270M

    C->>CA: POST /v1/chat/completions
    CA->>CA: WAF rules + rate limit check
    CA->>CW: HTTP request (allowed)
    CW->>CW: parse body, extract messages[]

    CW->>E: trigger inference::run_inference
    E->>IW: WebSocket RPC dispatch
    IW->>IW: apply_chat_template(messages)
    IW->>M: tokenize + generate (max 32k tokens)
    M-->>IW: token stream → decoded text
    IW-->>E: { output: "..." }
    E-->>CW: RPC result

    CW->>CW: wrap in OpenAI-compatible JSON
    CW-->>C: 200 { id, choices[{ message }] }

    Note over C,M: Total latency: ~500ms–3s on CPU (gemma-3-270m)
    Note over IW,M: Model loads once on boot,<br/>stays resident in RAM
